From 460c6e10b5e3e6061caf4c8fa2133500df549fb3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: ekane bryan <ekanebryan5@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 23 Jul 2026 09:54:58 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: WhatsApp share button, OG meta tags, registration
 capacity display
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

1. WhatsApp share: green WhatsApp button on event details page (next
   to Share). Opens wa.me with event title + link pre-filled. Drives
   organic viral growth on Cameroon's #1 messaging app.
2. Open Graph + Twitter Card meta tags in index.html: when someone
   shares ANY link from the app on WhatsApp/Facebook/Twitter, they now
   see a branded preview (logo, title, description) instead of a bare URL.
3. Registration capacity enforcement (frontend):
   - Shows 'Only N spots left!' warning when ≤5 spots remain.
   - Shows 'Sold out' + disables the register button when capacity is 0.
   - Hides the ticket purchase form when sold out.
   Backend already enforced capacity (abort 422) — this adds clear UX.
---
 Frontend/index.html                                | 11 ++++++++++-
 .../events/components/EventActionPanel.jsx         | 14 +++++++++++++-
 .../src/features/events/pages/EventDetailsPage.jsx |  3 ++-
 Frontend/src/shared/i18n/locales/en/common.json    |  6 ++++--
 Frontend/src/shared/i18n/locales/fr/common.json    |  6 ++++--
 5 files changed, 33 insertions(+), 7 deletions(-)

